+### MutableDependency
+
+Emitted when an immutable class inherits from a class or trait not marked immutable
+
+```php
+class MutableParent {
+    public int $i = 0;
+
+    public function increment() : void {
+        $this->i++;
+    }
+}
+
+/**
+ * @psalm-immutable
+ */
+final class NotReallyImmutableClass extends MutableParent {}
+```
+
